data.description: An extremely rare 5 bedroom property that has been updated and painted throughout. Live spaciously with this open floorplan, and a great backyard for entertaining. The property boasts high ceilings, lots of natural light, large room space, and the two-way stacked rock fireplace is truly the heart of this home. There is an eco-friendly gray water system that feeds the rose garden, and the patio includes an outdoor grill area and deck space for lounging. This home will be a great place to relax and spread out while enjoying all the conveniences of town! Schedule a showing today!
